                    <StackPanel MaxWidth="460">
                        <TextBlock TextWrapping="WrapWholeWords">
                            Mahjong is a great game. It's also complicated. 
                            I've been playing for about 12 years, and I still get confused, especially when it comes time to score a hand.
                            <LineBreak />
                            <LineBreak />
                            Also, Mahjong games tend to go on for a long time. 
                            One game goes on for many rounds. 
                            At family gatherings, we bring out a notebook with games dating back years, and try to find a match with whichever four people we happen to have together at that time.
                            <LineBreak />
                            <LineBreak />
                            I built this app to do 3 things: 
                            <LineBreak />
                            1.) Calculate scores quickly and easily
                            <LineBreak />
                            2.) Keep track of ongoing games
                            <LineBreak />
                            3.) Teach people how to play the game
                            <LineBreak />
                            <LineBreak />
                            I really created this app for myself and my friends and family, but I hope that you will find it useful as well. Enjoy!
